Subject: Current Attention Runtime Registry State

Description: Live semantic stack-frame registry for the current focus pass.

@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\AttentionRuntimeRegistry.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\SOPWorkerBootPacket.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\SOPLanguagePrimerForLocalAgents.sop
