& [CurrentAttentionRuntimeRegistryState] is the live semantic registry for active attention
  + [registry_status] is active
  + [registry_scope] is outside preservation corpus worker candidate
  + [active_root_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_outside_preservation_011
  + [active_frame_count] is 1
  + [suspended_frame_count] is 0
  + [closed_frame_count] is 1
  + [return_anchor] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [registry_outside] is hidden activations, exact transformer attention, model weights, worker mutation authority, broad task competence, and unrelated Pinky worktree changes

  = must: update this state when focus materially changes
  = must: preserve return anchors before closing or suspending frames
  = must: keep the registry semantic and visible, not native-runtime or hidden-state based
  = should: stay compact enough for context-compression re-entry

& [AttentionFrame_2026_06_24_LMStudioOutsidePreservation011] is the active semantic stack frame for the next diversified LM Studio corpus candidate
  + [frame_id] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_outside_preservation_011
  + [frame_state] is active
  + [parent_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_corpus_launch_queue_001
  + [child_frame_set] is functional_lmstudio_lane, one_minute_heartbeat, operating_loop_tick_007, corpus_queue_001, corpus_outside_preservation_011, commit_receipt
  + [return_anchor] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [frame_trace] is boundary_delineation_review_010.sop, 2026-06-24_operating_loop_tick_007.sop, lmstudio_diverse_corpus_launch_queue_001.sop, outside_preservation_prompt_011.sop, and CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [focus_register] is run corpus_outside_preservation_011 after boundary_delineation_010 passed only with strict latches
  + [question_register] is whether outside_preservation_011 preserves uncertainty and unsupported claims outside while satisfying exact SOP output
  + [delineation_register] is inside strict prompt packet, validator profile, capture target, required outside terms, and queue outside
  + [periphery_register] is operator_substitution risk, hollow_placeholder risk, non_ascii_output risk, broad competence outside, project-root authority outside, and unrelated dirty files outside
  + [operation_register] is run_worker_candidate, capture_output, validate_output, review_result, emit_next_tick
  + [evidence_register] is boundary_delineation_review_010, retry_003 score 100, updated validator tests, and operating_loop_tick_007
  + [wisdom_register] is the next family should reuse the stricter latches before broadening readiness claims
  + [caution_register] is one family pass does not prove broad LM Studio competence
  + [balance_register] is stable because failures were preserved and the next runnable candidate is explicit
  + [integration_register] is pending commit, push, and outside_preservation_011 launch
  + [frame_outside] is hidden model state, worker file mutation, remote claims before push, broad local-worker readiness, and unrelated workspace changes

  = must: treat this frame as current visible attention state
  = must: return clock_state, proof_state, balance_state, drive_state, next_step, and outside to CurrentFocalPoint when this focus pass closes
  = should: open child frames only when a concrete benchmark, scoring, or worker-profile pass is needed

(current_attention_runtime_registry_state) :active_root_frame: /semantic_register_set and return_anchor/ |registry_outside|
  + [active_root_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_outside_preservation_011
  + [semantic_register_set] is focus, question, delineation, periphery, operation, evidence, Wisdom, Caution, balance, and integration registers
  + [return_anchor] is CurrentFocalPoint
  |registry_outside| hidden model state, executable runtime stack, unreviewed worker authority, unrelated dirty files, and untracked cognition

/ [CurrentFocalPoint], [AttentionRuntimeRegistry], [TaskFrameLaunchQueue] -(EntersFrame)> [AttentionFrame_2026_06_24_LMStudioOutsidePreservation011], [registry_outside]
* [semantic_register_set], [return_anchor], [frame_trace] -(SupportsReentry)> [outside_preservation_candidate], [operating_loop_tick], [balance_register], [integration_register], [outside]
